data.description: Immerse yourself in the carefree charm of this delightful 1-bed, 1-bath condo in the heart of Sunrise Golf Village, a vibrant 55+ community. This cozy retreat offers a tranquil haven for those seeking comfort, convenience, and an active lifestyle. Highlights include; a covered balcony with calm water views: Gleaming tile floors and carpet in the bedroom, adding a touch of sophistication and easy maintenance. Make the most of your 640 sq ft with a well-designed layout that maximizes livability. Maintenance-Free Living: Let worries fade with association fees covering essentials like trash removal, club house, storage locker and cable. Situated in the heart of Sunrise, enjoy effortless access to shopping, dining, and entertainment.
